It’s time to take your first steps into the Digital World: Iliad. The Demo for Digimon Story Time Stranger is available now!

Game progress will carry over from the demo, so try it out today!

Travel across time and parallel worlds in this turn-based RPG when Digimon Story Time Stranger releases October 3rd, 2025 on PlayStation 5!

Pre-order Digimon Story Time Stranger to receive Agumon (Black), Gabumon (Black), and Uniform of a Certain School.

The Deluxe Edition includes the base game, plus Costume: Cyber Sleuth Set and the Season Pass featuring 3 DLC releases.

The Ultimate Edition includes Early Unlock for a special Agumon and special Gabumon with their Digivolution conditions already unlocked. The fastest way to get your hands on Agumon (Bond of Bravery) and Gabumon (Bond of Friendship)! Packed with a Season Pass, exclusive costumes, bonus items, and a nostalgic Cyber Sleuth BGM Pack—this is the definitive way
